text: Abdalla Haji Shaibu (born 21 October 1998) is a Tanzanian football player who most recently played as a defender for LA Galaxy II in the USL Championship, on loan from MFK Vyškov. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Tanzanian footballers Category:Tanzanian expatriate footballers Category:LA Galaxy II players Category:Association football defenders Category:USL Championship players Category:Expatriate soccer players in the United States
